mycollection.name: Pressed Foundation
mycollection.description: A pressed foundation by MarieNatie providing a silky and flawless finish – it provides great coverage and protects skin with SPF 10.  Titanium dioxide acts as an absorbent of oil and jojoba oil helps to cleanse and moisturize the skin.

mycollection.name: Mineral Blush
mycollection.description: Formulated to reduce the appearance of pores while creating a long-lasting natural finish.  This MarieNatie brush protects skin with SPF15.  Sericite mica is great for absorbing oil and won’t clog up pores.  Mica is a natural mineral that helps to enhance the skin tone.

mycollection.name: Proof It! Waterproof Mascara Top Coat
mycollection.description: With just two swipes our lash top coat transforms your favorite mascara from being conventional to waterproof! Our formula helps prevent clumping and leaves lashes looking gorgeous.
